<section id="aboutme" class="border-box h-100vh flex" tabindex="0">
    <div class="flex-1 flex fd-column jc-center">
        <h1 tabindex="0">Hi,<br>Renata Cotis<br>here!</h1>
        <p tabindex="0">I'm a <span class="bolder">Digital Illustrator</span>, although it took me a while to
            recognize myself as an artist. After two career
            changes, I realized that this profession and what it brings with it are what I value the most. It offers
            what I consider to be important aspects of life: geographic freedom, time liberty and the possibility to
            make a positive impact on people's lives. So, it would be a total pleasure <span class="bolder">to help
                    you tell a story</span>
            through
            <span class="bolder">illustrations</span>.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="column-right flex jc-end">
        <div class="img-container pos-relative">
            <img class="profile-photo" src="https://www.recotis.com/images/profile-photo-1000x750.webp"
                 alt="Renata smiles and sits on the grass at the Cliffs of Moher - Ireland." tabindex="0">
        </div>
    </div>
